（3）加TextActivity.java文件
		修改对应的布局文件activity_text.xml
		页面中加一Button按钮，实现点击时打开会话设置页，处理如下：
		@Override
		public void onClick(View v) {
			// TODO Auto-generated method stub
			if(v.getId() == R.id.button)
			{
		  		  Intent intent = new Intent(TextActivity.this, RongActivity.class);
		          intent.putExtra(RCloudConst.EXTRA.CONTENT, ConversationSettingFragment.class.getName());
		          startActivity(intent);
		          finish();
			}
		} 	
    	
